parameters.text:
=Classify this GDPR data subject request email and extract all relevant details.

From: {{ $json.from }}
Subject: {{ $json.subject }}
Body: {{ $json.text || $json.snippet }}

Determine if this is an access request (subject wants to see their data) or erasure request (subject wants data deleted). Extract the requester email and the data subject email (may differ if sent by a lawyer or agent).

parameters.jsCode:
const rows = $input.all();
const classify = $('Classify DSR Request').first().json.output || {};
const dbRecords = rows.filter(r => !r.json.error).map(r => r.json);
return [{ json: {
  request_type: classify.request_type,
  requester_email: classify.requester_email,
  requester_name: classify.requester_name,
  data_subject_email: classify.data_subject_email,
  request_summary: classify.request_summary,
  db_records: dbRecords,
  db_record_count: dbRecords.length
}}];

const rows = $input.all();
const ctx = $('Consolidate DB Results').first().json;
const crmRecords = rows.filter(r => !r.json.error).map(r => r.json.fields || r.json);
return [{ json: {
  ...ctx,
  crm_records: crmRecords,
  crm_record_count: crmRecords.length
}}];

parameters.text:
=Compile a comprehensive GDPR data report for the following request.

Request Type: {{ $json.request_type }}
Data Subject Email: {{ $json.data_subject_email }}
Requester: {{ $json.requester_name }} <{{ $json.requester_email }}>
Request Summary: {{ $json.request_summary }}

Database Records Found ({{ $json.db_record_count }}):
{{ JSON.stringify($json.db_records, null, 2) }}

CRM Records Found ({{ $json.crm_record_count }}):
{{ JSON.stringify($json.crm_records, null, 2) }}

Generate an email subject line and full HTML email body. For access requests, list all personal data found. For erasure requests, confirm what data will be deleted.
